{
  "stem": "1550.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then around 1930 or '31 or so, my mother had to get rid of her maid, and we didn't have been a maid anymore.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father had a very elegant store in this one of the main fancy shopping streets of Vienna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That store went-- it didn't go bankrupt but it didn't do well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father had to give it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So for a while he didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he, after about two years of doing various things, he eventually started another business, I think in 1935 or so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it was a difficult time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was also from-- there were also-- there was a lot of unrest in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In 1934, there were two revolutions in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In February there was a socialist revolution that had tried to overthrow the government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in July, there was a Nazi coup d'etat where the Nazis start to seize the government.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember those things well because, you know, it was such extraordinary occurrences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I remember those two events very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, life-- while life was more or less normal, there was a lot of anti-Semitism in Vienna, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And although, like I told you, I was not a-- we were not a religious family at all, but in retrospect, all my friends were Jews, you know, practically all of them, except one or two.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of my colleagues in school was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were living in a Jewish area, and looking over my class in my high school class where I went to, to the high school where I went for four years, I think all of my colleagues, with the exception of one, were Jews.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was a Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
